## 6. World-Building and Setting (out of 10):
Score: 6/10

The setting is described adequately to establish the geographical and cultural backdrop, but there is a lack of immersive detail that would bring the scene to life. More descriptive imagery and context about the setting could enhance engagement.

## Final Score:
66/100

## Overall Feedback:

The story provides a coherent historical recount of the Hijra, capturing the pivotal moments and significance in Islamic history. However, it could benefit from more creative storytelling techniques to distinguish it from textbook-style retellings. Enhancing character depth and employing more vivid descriptive language would improve emotional engagement and reader immersion. Improving these aspects could elevate the narrative from a straightforward recount to a compelling story.